VPlay written by &#8216;Crazy&#8217; MohanRendered by T.S.Balakrishna SastrigalT.S.Balakrishna Sastrigal takes listeners on a pilgrimage to the places Tyagaraja visited and composed songs on the deities. The places include Tiruvotriyur, Lalgudi, Kovur and Tirupati. Sastrigal&#8217;s elucidation includes  some of the most poignant songs connected to   incidents in Tyagaraja&#8217;s life. This recording is  extracted from one of the many concerts during Sastrigal&#8217;s U.S. trip in 1983.Conceived by Mala Mohan and presented by Guruvayur Dorai
